**Curse Caster** | Werewolf Power | Temporary
__Basics__
Each day, the Curse Caster may attempt to apply the accursed modifier to another player.
__Details__
During the day, the Curse Caster may select one player. If the player is not part of the wolfpack, the accursed modifier is applied on top of their current role.
Applying the accursed modifier is an immediate action.
If the the Curse Caster selects a member of the wolfpack, the action will fail and the Curse Caster will be informed why.
If the Curse Caster selects a target that is already accursed, the action will fail and the Cursed Caster will be informed. This is a different message than selecting a member of the wolfpack.
The Curse Caster is neither a lycan or a member of the wolfpack.

__Simplified__
Each day, the Curse caster can attempt to apply the accursed modifier to a player.
The Curse Caster and the wolfpack do not know each other. 
This action will fail on members of the wolfpack and the Curse Caster is informed why. 
